Company Overview of Baillie Gifford & Co Ltd



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Baillie Gifford & Co Ltd is a privately owned investment manager. The firm launches and manages equity, fixed income, and balanced mutual funds for its clients. It unvests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. The firm was founded in 1979 and is based in Edinburgh, Scotland with additional ofice in London, United Kingdom. Baillie Gifford & Co Ltd operates as a subsidiary of Baillie Gifford & Co.


